sentence: brennin james millirons, age 24, of akron, passed away saturday, june 6, 2015 at akron city hospital surrounded by his family.
funeral service will be held saturday, june 13, 2015 at 11 a. m. at macedonia baptist church, 940 mc.
kinley ave., akron, oh 44306, pastor lorenzo glenn officiating.
friends may visit at the church from 10 a. m. until time of service.
procession will form and condolences may be sent to 1251 weathervane lane #1d, akron, oh 44313.
com account has been set up for donations.
published in akron beacon journal from june 7 to june 11, 2015
